Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵 贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.25,0:00:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该这么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过我们在这房间里独处时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫对方名字的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.63,0:00:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.74,0:00:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你陪我做奇怪的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要习惯和男生相处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得花好多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 反正这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是说习惯就能习惯的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边我来收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦贵明同学去收拾一下那边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明…同学
Comment: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,// ----TEXT----
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处的时候要叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱~佳~的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是谁值日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己一个人在胡思乱想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说班长哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂面和凉面有啥不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚纠结这问题以致深夜未眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想班长说不定会知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我班长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长就是班长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了别叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫小牧同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我的名字叫小牧爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来班长是叫爱佳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫 叫我小牧就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当 便当
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还能吃 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学你去书库吃午饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一会儿见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.85,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我觉得很过意不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 吃吧 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 这个非常好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 用不着吃得那么急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你脸上沾着饭粒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙招待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我来喂你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛笑眯眯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没笑眯眯的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说什么张嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是在妄想给谁喂便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这样 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.22,0:07:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为道歉 就把我的便当给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 没事 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去买个新的面包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对味道又没影响 而且这是雄二的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是向坂同学的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.82,0:08:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜拳输了 就被当跑腿的使唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说被女生坐过的面包
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙反而会吃得津津有味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸上沾着饭粒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个绝对够大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看吗 要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看要看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高处的书就让我来放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学只是陪我练习而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽 虽然瞥见了 但没在看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为惩罚 我要拿你做实验对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是不可抗力的事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申诉驳回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好弄到些比较少见的茶叶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了点冰镇红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰镇红茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的做法是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用开水泡出红茶倒入冰镇的容器中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果做的不好的话会变得很浑浊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我先把茶水滤出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在冰箱里放了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也来一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的把我当实验对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿去穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不会留下什么污渍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放这稍微晾一下就会干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜 又让河野同学看到我丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢脸二连击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视上的星相占卜还说会有好事发生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书放这个书架上没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以 贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才还那么好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋 我没带伞哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠过来一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀就要淋湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠过来一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被别人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻站着干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了贵明 忘带伞了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就该时刻都准备周全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你伞靠过来点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别拉我伞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的伞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在妄想些奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳你要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕向坂同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月的活动预定表都写在这上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要好好看一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学 我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.76,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道当上副班长了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮一下忙的话就能快点做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们两个关系是不是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后两人单独在书库里久留不归
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 咻咻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了 只是在帮忙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 对对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向坂同学你别说奇怪的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄二你也来帮忙捡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拒绝得那么干脆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆 爽快的拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…刚才被大家取笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你指雄二说的那些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是口无遮拦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该这么叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当两人在这里独处的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把书打包好之后帮我泡杯茶吧 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天还有非常好吃的茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说小牧同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在时候也不早了 不会有人在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 也对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么事 爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是随便叫下你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说贵明同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊 雄二 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天老姐似乎要派很多学生会的活给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我就一个人躲在校舍的角落里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避风头避到很晚才回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 孤零零的我垂头丧气地走向校舍门口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在鞋箱附近看到了好事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳 和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 无论去哪我都会陪伴在贵明的左右
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你这是演的哪出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你和班长两人相互叫对方名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你们两个有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 快招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.27,0:17:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在帮忙整理书库而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那用得着相互叫名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是练习而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 什么练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练习就是 就是练习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神魂颠倒 得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是姐姐你最喜欢吃的炸虾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不来的话 我就都吃掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野贵明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 由真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你直呼爱佳的名字 却不直呼我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 由真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 由真？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.19,0:18:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你别以为你这么就算赢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小贵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 笹森同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须叫我花梨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话我就公开那个录像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珊瑚 小琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫珊瑚和琉璃就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我可不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么只要直呼我的名字就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 小珊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久寿川学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连久寿川学姐也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 草壁同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 露子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小贵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不叫我环啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 阿贵 木实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木实的话不是一直都叫木实的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕木实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环 环
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,环…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然老姐还是比较适合称呼后面加个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裂了 裂了 要裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来晚了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被雄二缠上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 今天这就结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想中止练习
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想今后你还是不要再来这里比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.54,0:21:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 加我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河 河野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又忘记带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…要是被别人看到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无情 让我淋雨回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样又会给河野同学添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了我不在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我今天还特意跑去书库
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却吃了小牧同学的闭门羹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 还是快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.05,0:22:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 最近雨真是频繁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意不能忘记带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被别人看到的话 又要被八卦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学讨厌和我一起被八卦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒没…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不靠过来一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀要淋湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的被别人看见的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:22:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小牧同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨已经停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 这不就是小牧同学的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我怎么又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳你帮我打伞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 要不要来我家喝杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵明同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.03,0:23:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱佳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了啊 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郁乃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这不是河野贵明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是成电灯泡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 郁乃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,// ----NEXT----
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.25,0:26:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.65,0:26:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西露法妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.68,0:26:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈露美妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.65,0:26:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依露法小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.36,0:26:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妹妹两个字去掉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.27,0:26:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我哈~露~美~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.39,0:26:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还叫人家小姐 真见外
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.26,0:26:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你们三位…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.62,0:26:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人应该把女仆机器人当仆人般直呼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.21,0:26:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将来要成为达令的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.33,0:26:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应叫我哈露美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.93,0:26:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能叫我依露法的话我会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.91,0:26:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你们在忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.50,0:26:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春夏阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.13,0:26:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贵
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.20,0:27:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我春~夏~就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.26,0:27:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连春夏阿姨也
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.83,0:27:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和阿贵谁跟谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.61,0:27:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是刚刚认识
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.16,0:27:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.73,0:27:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这不是相处时日长短的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.73,0:27:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.96,0:27:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令的爱才是最关键的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.25,0:27:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿贵还是婴儿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.89,0:27:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还经常帮他换尿布啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.99,0:27:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿布
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候阿贵的○○还是那样小巧玲珑 太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.57,0:27:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很 很小巧玲珑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.18,0:27:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上幼儿园的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.93,0:27:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路后会很寂寞地在我的胸口○○的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.76,0:27:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.25,0:27:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还经常一起洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.20,0:28:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿贵那时候真是的 总是○○还会○○
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.38,0:28:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我可从来都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.41,0:28:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.30,0:28:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的阿贵 连大人都要甘拜下风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.42,0:28:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是早熟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.64,0:28:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甘 甘拜下风
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.16,0:28:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀


